<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Arthur Kaplan lifts half year shr.</title>
<headline>Arthur Kaplan lifts half year shr.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-02-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>Half year ended December 31</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr, attrib (cts)     21.4	  vs 18.9</p>
<p>    Div (cts)		  -	    vs  -</p>
<p>    Attrib income	   4.36	  vs 2.90</p>
<p>    Pre-tax		   6.73	  vs 4.99</p>
<p>    Tax			 2.37	  vs 2.09</p>
<p>    Interest paid	   0.38	  vs 0.94</p>
<p>    Turnover		  39.01	 vs 31.81</p>
<p>Full name: Arthur Kaplan Jewellery Holdings Ltd</p>
<p>NOTE - The company said it was its policy not to pay an interim dividend. It cautioned that a disproportionate amount of profit is generated in the first half due to high sales over the festive season.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
